type="local"
addr="jonmsterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>After going to press, we have fixed the following mistakes:</fr:p><fr:ol><fr:li>In the definition of a logos, we mistakenly said that "colimits commute with finite limits" but we meant to say that they are preserved by pullback. We thank <fr:link
